# CODEOWNERS — forbidden-zone protection (ADR-005, CLAUDE.md "Forbidden zones",
# docs/edd.md §15.4). Mirrors CLAUDE.md's forbidden-zone list exactly; if they
# ever drift, CLAUDE.md is authoritative and this file should be corrected to
# match, not the reverse.
#
# This file alone enforces nothing: GitHub only requires code-owner review on
# a PR if branch protection is configured to require it, which is a repo
# setting the operator applies by hand, not a file in this tree.

